<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="freely-adv">freely <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'friːli/    美 /'friːli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>自由地；无拘束地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't let the children run freely on the road.
不要让孩子们在街上乱跑。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>通畅地；无阻碍地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Traffic is now <strong>moving</strong> more <strong>freely</strong> following an earlier accident.
早些时候的事故过后，现在交通通畅些了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>直率地；坦白地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>freely admit</strong> what I said was wrong.
我坦率地承认自己说错了。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>慷慨地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She gave freely to charity. 
她慷慨捐献善款。</p></div></div>